SET_HIGH_CAPTURE.desc:
mode=scope
title=0V to 5V Step

channels=1
# NS*TG= {1, 2, 5, 10, 20, 50, 100, 200, 500, 2000,400} #mS
timebase = 0
NS=100
TG=1
xaxis=time
y1=A1
ymin=-10
ymax=10


#Specify exponential curvefit instead of sine
fitmode=dsine
#Charging to 5V level
fitmax=5

rangeA1=true
